      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a car to tinker with? This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, making it a great opportunity for someone handy! While it definitely shows its age and will need some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic chance to own a vehicle at a very accessible price point. Roll up your sleeves and bring this one back to life!",
