    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. While it still starts, the engine exhibits a noticeable knock and the transmission has difficulty engaging certain gears. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several deep scratches and areas of rust, while the interior has sustained considerable damage over the years. This car is best suited as a project vehicle or for parts, as it will need major repairs to be safely roadworthy again.",
