      "description": "Presenting an automotive masterpiece in showroom-ready condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved, offering an unparalleled driving experience that mirrors its original delivery day. From the flawless finish of the exterior to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every detail reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. Fully serviced and mechanically absolute, this is an investment-grade opportunity for the driver who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48900.0,
